        "synopsis": {
            "value": "With Xiao Qi returning as an ambassador for her home planet, the couple embarks on another series of adventure on Earth.\n\nChai Xiao Qi and Fang Leng are about to usher in their happily ever after if not for the appearance of an alien rival who is under orders to break them up. Chai Xiao Qi's \"partner\" Jiang Shi Yi who also hails from her home planet has been ordered to forcibly\n\ntake her away on the day of her wedding to Fang Leng with the intention to brainwash her. Can our main couple overcome all odds to protect their love for each other?",
